description.en: Medics use nanite revivification to get allied forces back up on their feet and back into the battle.
Engineers use nanites to reconstruct damage that has been done to mechanized allies such as vehicles, MAX suits, and base turrets.
Medics can quickly heal damage that has been done to allied troops keeping in the fight longer.
Pilots of ground or air vehicles that have multiple seats with attached weaponry can earn kills made by their passengers.
